FuncDef: This command specifies the id of default retail service if there is no match found in VLAN to retail map configuration (specified by thevlancommand). For DSM and migrant, this command is only applicable for non-NAT stacks.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the identifier of the retail service to be used by default of a value in the retail service map of this interface. Values-1 to 2147483650.
